{
  "stem": "2966.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We used to crush the bones.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "There shouldn't be no sign of anything that the Germans did, that they killed people, when the-- because the Russians were marching east-- westward already.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that's how we had to destroy all the evidence of their cruelty.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And that's how I worked for 10 nights with Igor, digging out dead bodies from mass graves and burning them. 10 nights, which is like 100 years.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that, it was-- it's a wonder that they didn't liquidate us because they usually used to shoot people after something like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't at that point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sometimes in October, we were sent away to another camp by the name of Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Want me to spell it for you?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "G-R-O-- double-S-- hyphen-- R-O-S-E-N.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This camp till today is not very famous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very few people heard of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was the one of the most cruelest camps that you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was already in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That was one of the cruelest camps that you could imagine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If anybody would invented what they did with us, you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First when we got there, it was late October, I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took us, we-- took us to a big place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- everybody had to undress, throw everything away, whatever we brought with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went through a-- they checked us out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They even checked your rectum.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we stood a whole night on the outside, in the drizzling rain, naked, standing and waiting, I don't know for what.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The next day in the morning, they took us to the showers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "First, they shaved us again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They put disinfectants on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, naked, they issued us shirts, just long shirts.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
